{"word":"G2443 - ἵνα - hína - hin'-ah - Albeit","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἵνα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hína</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hin'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Albeit</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Conjunction / இணைப்புச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"இப்படி, இதெல்லாம், இந்த - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"where"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from the same as the former part of <a href=\"#/G1438 - ἑαυτοῦ - heautoû - heh-ow-too'/1438\">G1438</a> (through the <i>demonstrative</i> idea; compare <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a>); in order <i>that</i> (denoting the <i>purpose</i> or the <i>result</i>): - albeit, because, to the intent (that), lest, so as, (so) that, (for) to. Compare <a href=\"#/G3363 - ἵνα μή - hína mḗ - hin'-ah may/3363\">G3363</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}